Linux - create/delete file&dir:
---------------------------------
touch - creates a 0 byte empty file
cat > filename - create a file and allows to write
cat >> filename - append data to existing file data
mkdir - create a directory
tree - displays directory structure
rm - to remove a file
rm -f : force removal of a file(skips confirmation)
rmdir - remove a directory
rm -rf : force removal of a directory

